articles.title: Auburn backup QB Sean White arrested, accused of public intoxication
articles.description: Days after being reinstated following a two-game suspension, Auburn backup QB Sean White was arrested early Sunday morning on a public intoxication charge.

articles.title: Justice denied: The lynching of Robin White and an unprecedented confession
articles.description: His accuser lied. A killer named names. But justice was still denied to a black man murdered in Elmore County in 1901.
